headline: Countdown to Aflac (AFL) Q4 Earnings: Wall Street Forecasts for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Aflac (AFL), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended December 2025.
